text: Kidysh () is a rural locality (a village) in Akhunovsky Selsoviet, Uchalinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 119 as of 2010. There are 3 streets. == Geography == It is located 32 km from Uchaly, 7 km from Akhunovo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Uchalinsky District
title: Kidysh
